text: Amber Rolfzen (born August 25, 1994 in Papillion, Nebraska) is an American volleyball player who plays in the German Women's Volleyball League. == Playing career == She played for the University of Nebraska. She participated at the 2016–17 Women's CEV Cup, with Dresdner SC. ==Clubs== {| class="wikitable sortable" |- ! Club ! Country ! From !
